headline: Biotech stocks: Who wins and who loses if RFK, Jr. goes
summary: Investing.com -- RBC Capital said the potential departure of Health and Human Services Secretary Robert F. Kennedy Jr. could have wide-ranging implications for the biotech sector, with both winners and losers across therapeutic areas.
